@node "StripProb" "Strip - What problems are there?"
There are no problems/bugs currently known to be in Strip.

Some tips on use might help. If you type

        strip
 or
        strip - -

nothing will happen and your prompt won't return. To get it back press
either ``Ctrl C'' followed by ``Return'' or ``Ctrl \''.
@endnode

